quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,78,"Na Skaniyan so miyadn rkano ko manga kan´g, go so manga kaylay, go so manga gdagda: Na miyakayto ito a kapphanalamat iyo"
  23,79,"Go Skaniyan so miyarmbad rkano ko lopa, go Ron kano plimoda"
  23,80,"Go Skaniyan so Pphangoyag go Pphangimatay, go kapaar Iyan so gii kapakazambi o gagawii ago so dawndaw: Ino kano di pnggdagda"
  23,81,"Kna, ka pitharo iran so lagid o pitharo o miyangaoona"
  23,82,"Pitharo iran: \"Ino amay ka matay kami go mbaloy kami a botha, go manga tolan (a miyarophod), ba mataan! a skami na pagoyagn kami dn"
  23,83,Sabnsabnar a minidiyandi rkami skami ago so manga loks ami angkai gowani. Da ko ungkai inonta na manga iringa a kabokhag o miyangaoona
  23,84,"Tharoang ka: \"Antawaa i khirk ko lopa ago so matatago on, o skano na katawi niyo"
  23,85,"Na ptharoon iran dn a: \"Rk o Allah!\". Tharoang ka a: \"Ino kano di phananadm"
  23,86,"Tharoang ka: \"Antawaa i khirk ko manga langit a pito, go Khirk ko aras a mala"
  23,87,"Ptharoon iran dn a: \"Rk o Allah\". Tharoang ka a: \"Ino kano di phananggila"
  23,88,"Tharoang ka: \"Antawaa i sii sa tangan iyan so kapaar ko langowan taman, go skaniyan i ppakalinding, go da a phakarn on, o skano na katawi niyo"
  23,89,"Ptharoon iran dn a: \"Rk o Allah\". Tharoang ka: \"Na andamanaya i kapkhalimpang iyo"
  23,90,"Kna, ka initalingoma Mi kiran so bnar: Na mataan! a siran na titho a manga bokhag"
  23,91,"Da kowa so Allah sa wata Iyan, go da a miyabaloy a pd Iyan a tohan: O adn a pd Iyan na bisaan dn o oman i isa a tohan so inadn iyan, go pgsn dn o sabaad kiran so sabaad. Soti so Allah! mawatan ko iphropa iran"
  23,92,"Katawan Iyan so gaib ago so mapayag: Na maporo a ka-aawat Iyan ko ipphanakoto iran (On)"